I need that.

486
00:54:39.997 --> 00:54:41.599
(WOLF GROWLING)

487
00:54:44.569 --> 00:54:46.070
(KEDA GRUNTING)

488
00:54:50.440 --> 00:54:51.408
(GRUNTS)

489
00:54:54.846 --> 00:54:56.279
(WHINING)

490
00:55:00.785 --> 00:55:01.984
(CONTINUES WHINING)

491
