Stop looking at me!

496
00:55:19.536 --> 00:55:21.104
Go ahead!

497
00:55:23.507 --> 00:55:24.875
(WHINING)

498
00:55:47.363 --> 00:55:48.799
(WIND HOWLING)

499
00:56:09.652 --> 00:56:11.053
(PANTING)

500
00:56:26.936 --> 00:56:28.771
